              "description": "Customer needs help with a previous order, store information, delivery, refund, tracking, or any issue or question related to an existing order or store service.  \n\nExamples:  \n-Where is my order?\n-I want to track my order\n-I didn’t receive my package\n-I want a refund \n-What are your store hours?\n-I need help with my order"
            },
            {
              "category": "Order",
              "description": "Customer wants to buy a product, place a new order, ask about product price, availability, or purchase process.\n\nExamples:\n-I want to buy this product\n-What is the price?\n-How can I order? \n-Do you have this item in stock? \n-I want to place an order"
            }
          ]
        },
